OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FThe sister of a grandmother from
OL,7,FSomerset who died after vital surgery
OL,8,Fwas cancelled five times says the
OL,9,Fhospital trust "left my beloved sister
OL,10,Fto die".
OL,12,FSarah Crowley, from Yeovil, was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with choroidal malignant
OL,14,Fmelanoma - an aggressive, rare form of
OL,15,Feye cancer - in 2016.
OL,17,FThe mother-of-two was referred for
OL,18,Fsurgery at the Bristol Royal Infirmary
OL,19,F(BRI) in 2021 after scans showed the
OL,20,Fcancer had spread to her liver.
