OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FThe operation was cancelled and four
OL,7,Fsubsequent operations over the next
OL,8,Ffew weeks were also cancelled.
OL,10,FSarah died in May 2023 and her sister,
OL,11,FVerity Tebby, told the University
OL,12,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS Trust
OL,13,F(UHBW) - which runs the BRI - at a
OL,14,Fpublic board meeting that she was
OL,15,F"heartbroken".
OL,17,FVerity said: "Death is final, and I
OL,18,Fbelieve this is overlooked and
OL,19,Fdisregarded here.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/16
