OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"My sister was a gracious and kind
OL,7,Fperson, she saw the good in people,
OL,8,Fbut this was tested during this time.
OL,10,F"At the fifth cancellation, her
OL,11,Fcomment was 'I believe they are just
OL,12,Fcancelling me until I am no longer
OL,13,Fsurgically viable, that takes the
OL,14,Fdecision from them'.
OL,16,F"I would like you to think about that
OL,17,Fand reflect on how you would feel if
OL,18,Fit were you or a loved one, because it
OL,19,Fappears not one person did.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/16
