CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"Your hospital admitted to failings
OL,7,Fand admitted to failing her.
OL,9,F"You were sorry but that holds no
OL,10,Fweight when I witnessed first-hand the
OL,11,Funbearable, unrelenting, cruel mental
OL,12,Ftorture of someone simply trying to
OL,13,Flive.
OL,15,F"From the point of the routine scan
OL,16,Fand the suspicion of the lesion
OL,17,Fconfirmed, I have lived through this
OL,18,Fdreadful ordeal with my sister.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/16
