OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FAfter her surgeries were repeatedly
OL,7,Fcancelled, Sarah turned to the Royal
OL,8,FFree Hospital in London to have it
OL,9,Fdone there.
OL,11,FFurther scans following that surgery
OL,12,Frevealed it had spread and the only
OL,13,Freal option was a treatment called
OL,14,Fchemosaturation, which is not funded
OL,15,Fon the NHS.
OL,17,FVerity said the delays at the BRI
OL,18,Fmeant it was too late for less
OL,19,Finvasive treatments and that her time
OL,20,Fhad been "squandered".
