OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FShe said that in a desperate attempt
OL,7,Fto at least live through the summer of
OL,8,F2023, Sarah opted for immunotherapy.
OL,10,FHowever, she had been reluctant to
OL,11,Fhave it because of the side-effects
OL,12,Fbut that she was then not strong
OL,13,Fenough to endure this and died after
OL,14,Fher second course of it.
OL,16,FVerity set up a GoFundMe page to help
OL,17,Ffund chemosaturation which can extend
OL,18,Fpatient's lives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/16
