OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FVerity said the family remained in
OL,7,Fserious debt after funding three
OL,8,Fcourses at the Spire Hospital in
OL,9,FSouthampton, costing a total of
OL,10,F#120,000.
OL,12,FShe told the board meeting on Tuesday
OL,13,F14 May: "None of this would have been
OL,14,Fconsidered by your staff who dismissed
OL,15,Fthe urgency and merely satisfied your
OL,16,Fcriteria for rebooking within the
OL,17,Frequired time frame.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/16
