OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"Sarah could not even bear the mention
OL,7,Fof Bristol as the trauma of what that
OL,8,Frepresented was too overwhelming for
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,F"I liken her situation to the sheep
OL,12,Ftrailers we've all sat alongside in
OL,13,Ftraffic, looking through the sides
OL,14,Fheading for the slaughterhouse or
OL,15,Fmarket to meet the same fate.
OL,17,F"The farmer may feel some pang of
OL,18,Fremorse the first few times he drops
OL,19,Fthem off and then becomes detached and
OL,20,Funaffected.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/16
