CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"This is how she was treated, but she
OL,7,Fwas someone's wife, mother, sister and
OL,8,Fdaughter.
OL,10,F"You are meant to be in the business
OL,11,Fof saving lives, yet we saw no
OL,12,Fevidence of this.
OL,14,F"I can honestly say I am forever
OL,15,Fchanged by these events and will
OL,16,Fremember your hospital as the one that
OL,17,Fleft my beloved sister to die."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/16
