OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FVerity said that with no guarantee of
OL,7,Fany of the five scheduled operations
OL,8,Fgoing ahead at the BRI, Sarah was
OL,9,F"simply left to it" and that no one
OL,10,Ffrom the trust contacted her other
OL,11,Fthan to rebook the surgery.
OL,13,FVerity said the family also did not
OL,14,Fhear back from staff despite asking
OL,15,Fnumerous times for medics to request
OL,16,Fspecial funding from the NHS for
OL,17,Fchemosaturation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/16
