OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FShe said: "The time was squandered.
OL,7,FNot one person in Bristol helped her,
OL,8,Fthey just kept cancelling and
OL,9,Frebooking.
OL,11,F"It was a catalogue of disasters. She
OL,12,Fwas dying. She was trying to find
OL,13,Fevery which way to live, but they left
OL,14,Fher to die."
OL,16,FBRI boss: 'I apologise to you for
OL,17,Fdelays in your sister's care - it's
OL,18,Fnot acceptable'
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/16
