OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,FUHBW interim chief executive Stuart
OL,7,FWalker told Verity: "That's an
OL,8,Fincredibly powerful story and a hugely
OL,9,Fhonest reflection of your, your
OL,10,Fsister's and your family's experience.
OL,12,F"It's important having heard that
OL,13,Fstory on behalf of the organisation
OL,14,Fthat I apologise to you for delays in
OL,15,Fyour sister's care and for the
OL,16,Fexperience that she encountered.
OL,18,F"It's not acceptable to suffer those
OL,19,Fdelays. We will do everything in our
OL,20,Fpower to prevent a recurrence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/16
