OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"A number of lessons have been learned
OL,7,Ffrom your sister's case and we will
OL,8,Fcontinue to learn lessons."
OL,10,FTrust chief nurse and midwife Deirdre
OL,11,FFowler said afterwards: "We are
OL,12,Fsincerely sorry for the distress and
OL,13,Fupset caused by the cancellations of
OL,14,FMrs Sarah Crowley's surgery, and the
OL,15,Fimpact this has had on Mrs Verity
OL,16,FTebby, and their family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/16
