PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717106480
OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"This is not the experience we wish
OL,7,Ffor anyone in our care, and on behalf
OL,8,Fof the whole organisation, I want to
OL,9,Fapologise for the experience that the
OL,10,Ffamily encountered with us.
OL,12,F"We take patient and family member
OL,13,Fconcerns and complaints very
OL,14,Fseriously, and we have reviewed our
OL,15,Fprocesses and put improvements in
OL,16,Fplace to address the issues raised.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/16
