OL,3,CGrandmother died after cancer surgery
OL,4,Ccancelled five times
OL,6,F"We bring patient stories to begin
OL,7,Fboard meetings to inform and ground
OL,8,Fdirectors' understanding of the impact
OL,9,Fof the lived experience for our
OL,10,Fpatients, as well as the experience of
OL,11,Four staff and organisational culture.
OL,13,F"I want to personally thank Mrs Verity
OL,14,FTebby for sharing her incredibly
OL,15,Fmoving and powerful story which has
OL,16,Foffered us valuable learnings that we
OL,17,Fhave, and will continue to improve on."
